			<h3 ><a href="#p79968">Re: Frustrated... battery or dead roomba?</a></h3>
			<p class="author"><a href="./viewtopic.php?p=79968&amp;sid=53e7b36b35ea6b46b92edecdde9af8ac#p79968"><img src="./styles/robotreviews/imageset/icon_post_target.gif" width="11" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" /></a>by <strong><a href="./memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=1074&amp;sid=53e7b36b35ea6b46b92edecdde9af8ac">vic7767</a></strong> &raquo; July 2nd, 2010, 5:36 pm </p>

			

